Class ResponseJDBCAccessLogValve

All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.management.MBeanRegistration, org.apache.catalina.Contained, org.apache.catalina.Lifecycle, org.apache.catalina.Valve
public class ResponseJDBCAccessLogValve
extends JDBCAccessLogValve

An extension of JDBCAccessLogValve that avoids reflection when a few operationally important values of HTTP queries are exposed to the Valves getting org.apache.catalina.connector.Response.

Development

This Valve was used with PostgreSQL 9.1 UTF8 on Mac OS X 10.6 (Snow Leopard) and the Apple distribution of Oracle Java 1.6 originally.
